Insperity
Insperity is a company that specializes in providing a comprehensive range of employee benefits packages and support services. It offers various benefits aimed at improving employee well-being and satisfaction. These include programs such as the Employee Assistance Program (EAP), caregiver support, and a Health Care Flexible Spending Account Plan. Furthermore, Insperity provides Adoption Assistance Programs to assist employees in navigating the adoption process.

In addition to these offerings, Insperity supplies a variety of insurance products, which encompass Health Savings Accounts (HSAs) and disability insurance. The organization focuses on health care support by providing health insurance options to its clients, including high deductible health plans (HDHP) and other medical services. Moreover, Insperity ensures that eligible employees have access to essential coverage, including dental and vision plans, available nationwide for employees and their dependents. 

Overall, Insperity plays a significant role as an employer service provider, delivering essential benefits that cater to the diverse needs of its workforce, thereby enhancing employee well-being through a holistic approach to employee support and health care services.
